description:
A customized GUNPLA which adds elements of the http://anidb.net/ch112414 [SD Command Gundam] to the [url=http://anidb.net/ch23186]00 Qan[T][/url]. As well as improved defenses thanks to its extra armor, it has many new weapons designed for both long- and short-range use, enabling it to fight in any situation.
Source: gundam.info
name: Gundam 00 Command Qan[T]
